        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【教师】关于开展未来教师工作坊（第十二期）——百步梯学堂“课程中心”平台AI辅助课程建设培训的通知]]></title>
            <link>https://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/cms/article/view.do?type=posts&amp;id=eec18a7b9dfc61df019eee17e67500d9</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">scut-jw-eec18a7b9dfc61df019eee17e67500d9</guid>
            <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 08:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong>类型:</strong> 教师 | <strong>日期:</strong> 2026.06.22 | <a href="https://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/cms/article/view.do?type=posts&id=eec18a7b9dfc61df019eee17e67500d9">查看原文</a></p><hr><div class="content">



<p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom:10px;text-align:center;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><br/></p><p><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px">各院（系）：</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">为落实国家教育数字化战略行动，推动人工智能赋能教育转型，促进信息技术与教育教学深度融合，助力我校教师</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">AI辅助课程建设工作，学校将继续开展未来教师工作坊，具体安排如下：</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px">一、</span><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 19px">培训时间及地点</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px">1.2026年6月24日（星期三），下午14:30—17:30，地点为五山校区一号楼1511培训室。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px">2. 2026年6月26日（星期五），下午14:30—17:30，地点为五山校区一号楼1511培训室。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px">两次课程内容一致，老师可自行选择参加。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 19px">二、培训内容</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px">1. 介绍校内部署平台百步梯学堂“课程中心”课程网站快速建设及应用：各模块的功能介绍，包含课程信息、课程资源、知识/问题/能力图谱、教学活动的作业、签到、讨论、测试和问卷等。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px">2. 介绍AI辅助课程建设的标准要求与实施路径。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px">3. 介绍新功能：作业的AI辅助批改和定位签到功能。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px">4. 平台AI功能应用：AI生图，AI出题，OCR功能，文档AI功能，视频AI功能，RAG知识库构建。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 19px">三、工作要求</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px">1.请各学院（系）积极发动老师报名参加,报名链接为</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><a href="https://ecourse.scut.edu.cn/web/templet/userGroup/joinPage.html?wangZhanID=64273&amp;menuID=457346"><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family: 等线;color: rgb(70, 120, 134);font-size: 19px">https://ecourse.scut.edu.cn/web/templet/userGroup/joinPage.html?wangZhanID=64273&amp;menuID=457346</span></span></a></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px">2.请报名参加的老师提前10分钟到场签到。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px">4</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px">.本次培训将计入新教师研习营主题研讨学分,其他教师参加本次培训可计入教师三年轮训计划学时。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">联系人：王老师，联系电话：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">87111089-12。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:等线;font-size:14px"> </span></p><p><span style=";font-family:等线;font-size:14px"> </span></p><p style="text-align:right"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px">本科生院</span></p><p style="text-align:right"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:19px">2026年6月22日</span></p><p><br/></p>
</div>]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【信息】关于选拔2023级部分优秀本科生进入辅修学士学位毕业设计（论文）环节的通知]]></title>
            <link>https://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/cms/article/view.do?type=posts&amp;id=eec18a7b9dfc61df019ed841b5dc00d7</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">scut-jw-eec18a7b9dfc61df019ed841b5dc00d7</guid>
            <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 08:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong>类型:</strong> 信息 | <strong>日期:</strong> 2026.06.18 | <a href="https://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/cms/article/view.do?type=posts&id=eec18a7b9dfc61df019ed841b5dc00d7">查看原文</a></p><hr><div class="content">



<p style=";margin-bottom:0;line-height:40px"><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">各院（系）：</span></p><p style=";margin-bottom:0;text-indent:40px;line-height:40px"><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">辅修专业、微专业是为了培养复合型人才而设置，以鼓励学有余力的学生在完成主修专业学习任务的前提下，向多学科发展。根据《华南理工大学全日制本科学生辅修专业及辅修学士学位管理办法》（华南工教[2025]15号）、</span><span style="font-size:21px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">广州国际校区全日制本科学生辅修专业及辅修学士学位管理办法》(国际校区[2025]4号)文件精神</span><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">，结合学校实际情况，选拔2023级部分优秀本科生进入辅修学士学位毕业设计（论文）环节。</span></p><p style=";margin-bottom:0;text-indent:40px;line-height:40px"><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">现将有关事项通知如下：</span></p><p style=";margin-bottom:0;text-indent:40px;line-height:40px"><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">1.</span><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">选拔对象：修读辅修专业的2023级学生（含建筑学院、医学院五年制2022级本科生）。</span></p><p style=";margin-bottom:0;text-indent:40px;line-height:40px"><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">2.</span><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">选拔条件：无任何未解除的违法违纪处分；修读辅修学士学位的学生前六学期（五年制前八学期）主修专业必修课程平均成绩（首次考核成绩、已出分课程成绩）75分以上（含75分），且所修读辅修课程学分（含本学期正在修读的课程学分）超过辅修学士学位培养计划要求总学分的80％。</span></p><p style=";margin-bottom:0;text-indent:40px;line-height:40px"><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">3.</span><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">选拔程序：</span></p><p style=";margin-bottom:0;text-indent:40px;line-height:40px"><strong><span style="font-size:20px;font-family: 仿宋;color:black">学生申请及院（系）审核阶段、汇总提交：</span></strong><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">6</span><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">月18日－6月30日，符合条件的学生填写《华南理工大学2023级本科生进入辅修学士学位毕业设计（论文）环节申请表》（见附件1），申请人必须如实填写申请表中各项内容，并及时交辅修学院教务员审核汇总，逾期不接受补报。</span></p><p style=";margin-bottom:0;text-indent:40px;line-height:40px"><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">辅修学院收到材料后复审学生的辅修学分，并做好汇总表（附件2），于7月2日之前报送本科生院教务科。</span></p><p style=";margin-bottom:0;text-indent:40px;line-height:40px"><strong><span style="font-size:20px;font-family: 仿宋;color:black">本科生院公示及确认阶段：</span></strong><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">7</span><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">月5日前，本科生院审核并在教务管理系统公布2023级本科生进入辅修学士学位毕业设计（论文）环节的学生名单。</span></p><p style=";margin-bottom:0;text-indent:40px;line-height:40px"><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">辅修学院安排学生于2026-2027学年度第一学期完成辅修学士学位毕业设计（论文）。</span></p><p style=";margin-bottom:0;text-indent:40px;line-height:40px"><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black"></span></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img src="http://110.65.10.251:8089/zhinan/res/cms/lib/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;"/><a href="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/file/20260618/1781744613391037000.doc" style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" title="附件1：华南理工大学2023级本科生进入辅修学士学位毕业设计（论文）环节申请表.doc.doc">附件1：华南理工大学2023级本科生进入辅修学士学位毕业设计（论文）环节申请表.doc.doc</a></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img src="http://110.65.10.251:8089/zhinan/res/cms/lib/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_txt.gif" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;"/><a href="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/file/20260618/1781744619114070476.xlsx" style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" title="附件2：2023级进入辅修学士学位毕设环节报名汇总表（原）.xlsx">附件2：2023级进入辅修学士学位毕设环节报名汇总表（原）.xlsx</a></p><p style=";margin-bottom:0;text-indent:40px;line-height:40px"><br/></p><p style=";margin-bottom:0;text-indent:40px;line-height:40px"><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black"> </span></p><p style="margin-top:5px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:5px;margin-left:0;text-align:right"><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">本科生院</span></p><p style="margin-top:5px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:5px;margin-left:0;text-align:right"><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">2026</span><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black">年6月18日</span></p><p style=";margin-bottom:0;text-indent:40px;line-height:40px"><strong><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:仿宋;color:black"> </span></strong></p><p><br/></p>
</div>]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【信息】关于报送2026年暑假“虚拟第三学期”开课计划的通知]]></title>
            <link>https://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/cms/article/view.do?type=posts&amp;id=eec18a7b9dfc61df019ed32226f500d5</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">scut-jw-eec18a7b9dfc61df019ed32226f500d5</guid>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 08:05:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong>类型:</strong> 信息 | <strong>日期:</strong> 2026.06.17 | <a href="https://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/cms/article/view.do?type=posts&id=eec18a7b9dfc61df019ed32226f500d5">查看原文</a></p><hr><div class="content">



<p><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px">各院（系）：</span></p><p style="text-indent: 40px;line-height: 40px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">为进一步变革传统课程修读模式，</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px">通过信息技术与教学内容的深度融合，</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">延展学生有效学习时间，创新更加自由、充实与高效的人才培养模式，学校于</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">2026年暑假</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">继续实施开设</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">“虚拟第三学期”</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px">。</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">现将开课要求通知如下：</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 40px;line-height: 40px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">1.“虚拟第三学期”以大规模在线开放课程（MOOC）教学为载体，建立“循环开课、自主修读、统一考核”的修读模式，学生学习线上资源，参与在线活动，完成在线作业和考试，总分达到考核标准后获得学分，所有学习活动均在线上进行。学生完成所有网上学习环节并考核合格后，方可获得相应的学分。</span></span><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 20px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">每个学生最多可通过</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">“虚拟第三学期”认定4学分的通识课程学分。</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 43px;line-height: 40px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">2.此次“虚拟第三学期”开设的课程仅面向通识课程，并已在平台上线使用，包括我校自建和引进课程。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px;line-height: 40px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">3.开课时间：202</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">6</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">年</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">7</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">月</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">20</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">日至</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">202</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">6</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">年</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">8</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">月</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">28</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">日，共计</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">6</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">周。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px;line-height: 40px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">4.实行课程负责人制。课程负责人负责课程上线、课程的资源更新及教学秩序维护，为学习者提供优质的教学支持服务和个性化指导，关注学习者的评价和反馈，并持续对上线课程进行改进和优化。课程资源应包括课程介绍、负责人介绍、教学大纲、授课视频、演示文稿、教学课件、课程公告、测验和作业、考试等教学活动必需的资源，以及满足高校教学和学习者自主学习需求的参考资料。通过课程平台，教师为学习者提供测验、作业、考试、答疑、讨论等教学组织活动，及时开展在线指导与测评。各项教学活动完整、有效，按计划实施，学习者在线学习响应度高，师生互动充分，能有效促进师生之间、学生之间进行资源共享、互动交流和自主式与协作式学习。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px;line-height: 40px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">5.</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">为提升课程教学质量和小班化教学水平，加强课堂互动交流，同时为鼓励学生修读更加多样化的课程，</span></span><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-size: 20px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">每教学班人数上限为</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-size: 20px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">90</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-size: 20px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">人，每位老师最多开设</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-size: 20px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">2</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-size: 20px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">个教学班</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px;line-height: 40px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">6.请课程负责人于202</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">6</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">年</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">6</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">月</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">24</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">前报送</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">202</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">6</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">年</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">暑假</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">“虚拟第三学期”开课计划表（附件1）、课程修读要求（附件2），课程修读要求必须明确线上教学内容学习时间节点和要求，并严格执行。所有附件材料纸版一式一份交至五山校区笃行楼307，电子版发送至xhui@scut.edu.cn。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px;line-height: 40px"><span style=";font-family:Helvetica;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px"> </span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px;line-height: 40px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">联系人：肖老师，联系电话：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">87110727。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px;line-height: 40px"><span style=";font-family:Helvetica;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-size:20px"> </span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px;line-height: 40px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">附件：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">1.</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">2026年暑假</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">“虚拟第三学期”开课计划表</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 100px;line-height: 40px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">2.</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">2026年暑假</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">“虚拟第三学期”课程修读要求</span></span></p><p style="text-align:right;line-height:40px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:20px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"> </